  <brief_title>Study of Nifurtimox to Treat Refractory or Relapsed Neuroblastoma or Medulloblastoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial of Nifurtimox for Refractory or Relapsed Neuroblastoma or Medulloblastoma.</official_title>
